### Get all classics
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/classics

### Get all classics with a specific language preference (e.g., German)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/classics?lang=de

### Get content for a specific classic story by slug (English)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/classics/story/little-red-riding-hood

### Get content for a specific classic story by slug with a specific language (e.g., German)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/classics/story/little-red-riding-hood?lang=de